reviews.text: The train service is awful loads of cancellations all the time. The black guy that does the gates however is awesome, always helpful. Positive. And has a nice smile

The ticket officer (kowsar) is extremely unprofessional, it is hard to believe he’s been working at this station for so long. He is rude beyond belief, shouts at customers and demonstrates that he gets extremely irritated when asked questions by travellers. He is constantly on the phone/computer doing his private stuff and watching videos. On top of all, the service is disgusting, trains are running late or getting cancelled every single day.  It’s 2018, sort it!!

The Ticket office clerk named kowsar, who is always late, closes the ticket office to prey during working hours 5 times per shift. 

Does not refund money to customers taken by machines, instead claims the money fraudulently for him self. 

Wonders off multiple times through out his shift to get his hair cut and to do personal shopping at Morrison's. leaving customers frustrated. 

Because he is friends with a certain manager he is allowed to continue his appalling behaviour and lazy work ethic. 

Shame on you great northern Rail for allowing him to continue getting paid for a less than poor service. 

Watching football on his mobile disrespectfully in front of customers needing to purchase tickets. keeping them waiting unnecessarily. Then sending them to wrong destination. absolutely appalling.

Remove my review and I shall never post again as I don't want to be apart of a service protecting those who are making peoples lifes miserable. CCTV DOESNT LIE
